@startuml C4-Context
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Context.puml

title English Learning App - System Context Diagram

Person(user, "English Learner", "Traditional Chinese speaker learning English vocabulary")

System(englishApp, "English Learning App", "Android application for learning English vocabulary with spaced repetition")

System_Ext(cambridgeAPI, "Cambridge Dictionary API", "External API providing English to Traditional Chinese translations")

System_Ext(androidSystem, "Android OS", "Operating system providing device services and storage")

Rel(user, englishApp, "Uses", "Searches words, practices vocabulary")
Rel(englishApp, cambridgeAPI, "Fetches definitions", "HTTPS/REST API")
Rel(englishApp, androidSystem, "Uses", "Local storage, UI framework")

note right of englishApp
  **Primary Features:**
  - Word search with Traditional Chinese translations
  - 6-stage spaced repetition system
  - Offline vocabulary storage
  - Progress tracking
end note

note right of cambridgeAPI
  **API Base URL:**
  https://dictionary-api.eliaschen.dev/
  
  **API Endpoint:**
  /api/dictionary/en-tw/{word}
  
  **Response includes:**
  - Word definitions with Traditional Chinese translations
  - Part of speech information
  - Example sentences (English + Chinese)
  - Pronunciation data with audio URLs
  - Verb forms (if applicable)
end note

@enduml
